Created by PLY version 3.11 (http://www.dabeaz.com/ply)

Grammar

Rule 0     S' -> programa
Rule 1     lamda -> <empty>
Rule 2     programa -> sentencia
Rule 3     programa -> sentencia NEW_LINE programa
Rule 4     sentencia -> INT_VALUE operand INT_VALUE
Rule 5     operand -> PLUS
Rule 6     operand -> MINUS

Terminals, with rules where they appear

INT_VALUE            : 4 4
MINUS                : 6
NEW_LINE             : 3
PLUS                 : 5
error                : 

Nonterminals, with rules where they appear

lamda                : 
operand              : 4
programa             : 3 0
sentencia            : 2 3

Parsing method: LALR

state 0

    (0) S' -> . programa
    (2) programa -> . sentencia
    (3) programa -> . sentencia NEW_LINE programa
    (4) sentencia -> . INT_VALUE operand INT_VALUE

    INT_VALUE       shift and go to state 3

    programa                       shift and go to state 1
    sentencia                      shift and go to state 2

state 1

    (0) S' -> programa .



state 2

    (2) programa -> sentencia .
    (3) programa -> sentencia . NEW_LINE programa

    $end            reduce using rule 2 (programa -> sentencia .)
    NEW_LINE        shift and go to state 4


state 3

    (4) sentencia -> INT_VALUE . operand INT_VALUE
    (5) operand -> . PLUS
    (6) operand -> . MINUS

    PLUS            shift and go to state 6
    MINUS           shift and go to state 7

    operand                        shift and go to state 5

state 4

    (3) programa -> sentencia NEW_LINE . programa
    (2) programa -> . sentencia
    (3) programa -> . sentencia NEW_LINE programa
    (4) sentencia -> . INT_VALUE operand INT_VALUE

    INT_VALUE       shift and go to state 3

    sentencia                      shift and go to state 2
    programa                       shift and go to state 8

state 5

    (4) sentencia -> INT_VALUE operand . INT_VALUE

    INT_VALUE       shift and go to state 9


state 6

    (5) operand -> PLUS .

    INT_VALUE       reduce using rule 5 (operand -> PLUS .)


state 7

    (6) operand -> MINUS .

    INT_VALUE       reduce using rule 6 (operand -> MINUS .)


state 8

    (3) programa -> sentencia NEW_LINE programa .

    $end            reduce using rule 3 (programa -> sentencia NEW_LINE programa .)


state 9

    (4) sentencia -> INT_VALUE operand INT_VALUE .

    NEW_LINE        reduce using rule 4 (sentencia -> INT_VALUE operand INT_VALUE .)
    $end            reduce using rule 4 (sentencia -> INT_VALUE operand INT_VALUE .)

